FireUp is a skeleton of Firefox 3.6.*/4.0b8pre-compatible extension. Within you
shall find the established directory and file structure with top-level folders
for XPCOM components ("components"), JavaScript code modules ("modules"), and
plugins ("plugins"). Overlay script ensures: extension startup; initialization
of preference branch, preference listener and string bundle access; proper
shutdown.

MIT license is used throughout the code.

Developed by Dmitriy Khudorozhkov (dmitriy.khudorozhkov@gmail.com).